            <fr:title text="Thread">Thread</fr:title>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter><html:p>An independent unit of execution within a <fr:link href="/FCHM/" title="Process" uri="https://kellenkanarios.com/FCHM/" display-uri="FCHM" type="local">Process</fr:link>. Each thread has its own program counter, register set, and stack — but shares the surrounding address space, file descriptors, and other process-level resources with its siblings.</html:p><html:p>To support a <fr:link href="/OKCI/" title="Context switch" uri="https://kellenkanarios.com/OKCI/" display-uri="OKCI" type="local">context switch</fr:link> between threads, the OS keeps a <html:em>thread control block</html:em> (TCB) per thread — the per-thread analog of <fr:link href="/JE53/" title="Process control block" uri="https://kellenkanarios.com/JE53/" display-uri="JE53" type="local">Process control block</fr:link>. Each thread also gets its own stack within the process's address space.</html:p><html:p>Why threads instead of processes:</html:p><html:ol><html:li><html:em>Intra-process parallelism</html:em>: parallelizable work within one program, without paying the <fr:link href="/OKCI/" title="Context switch" uri="https://kellenkanarios.com/OKCI/" display-uri="OKCI" type="local">context switch</fr:link> cost of separate processes.</html:li>
  <html:li><html:em>Avoiding blocking I/O</html:em>: one thread blocks waiting on I/O while others keep running.</html:li></html:ol>
 <html:div class="jms-callout" style="
  margin: 1em 0 1em 0.25em;
  padding: 0.5em 1.1em 0.5em 1.2em;
  border-left: 4px solid rgba(90, 90, 110, 0.7);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  background-color: rgba(90, 90, 110, 0.05);
  "><html:span style="font-weight: 600; color: rgba(90, 90, 110, 0.7);">Remark.</html:span> Sharing an <fr:link href="/7MH4/" title="Address space" uri="https://kellenkanarios.com/7MH4/" display-uri="7MH4" type="local">address space</fr:link> is exactly what makes threads cheap to communicate between and exactly what makes them dangerous — see <fr:link href="/VOQN/" title="Race condition" uri="https://kellenkanarios.com/VOQN/" display-uri="VOQN" type="local">Race condition</fr:link> and <fr:link href="/KG2K/" title="Critical section" uri="https://kellenkanarios.com/KG2K/" display-uri="KG2K" type="local">Critical section</fr:link>.</html:div>
</fr:mainmatter>
